data.description:
This fantastic three-bedroom home with some great features. The master bedroom's large walk-in closet and siting parlor, carpeted floors throughout the house must add a lot of comfort. Having an office or study, open living area, and a formal dining room sounds perfect for various needs. The big kitchen with granite tops and an island, along with the den with a fireplace, would be great for both cooking and relaxation.

The covered patio with a jacuzzi and access to acres of trees, an above-ground pool, and a homemade fire pit sounds like a perfect place for entertainment and relaxation. The covered RV parking and gated property offer practicality and security. It sounds like a wonderful place to call home!
We also have two large storage  building. not to forget about Chicken coop for this country life country living.
